You have to conquer more territory than your opponent. One cell with your color = one point for you. You can totally steal the cells of the other dino!

Player One, press Z to go up, S to go down, Q to go left and D to go right.

Player Two, press Up to go up, Down to go down, Left to go left and Right to go right.

Game: camcharp Icons: Arks Music: 8 Bit Universe
